OL,3,C'My girl had to die to be heard':
OL,4,CMum's plea for change in law
OL,6,FThe mother of a young woman who took
OL,7,Fher own life after years of domestic
OL,8,Fabuse has issued a plea for urgent
OL,9,Flegal changes, saying her daughter
OL,10,F"had to die to be heard".
OL,12,FKiena, 23, from Fleetwood, Lancashire,
OL,13,Fwas abused and coercively controlled
OL,14,Fby her former partner Ryan Wellings
OL,15,Fand, despite reaching out for help
OL,16,Fmultiple times, took her own life in
OL,17,FJuly 2022.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
