OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784656151
OL,3,C'My girl had to die to be heard':
OL,4,CMum's plea for change in law
OL,6,FAngela Dawes, Kiena's mother, is
OL,7,Furging the public to back the campaign
OL,8,Ffor Kiena's Law which would make
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse-related suicide a
OL,10,Fspecific criminal offence.
OL,12,FSpeaking four years on from her
OL,13,Fdaughter's death, Angela described the
OL,14,Fdaily pain of raising Kiena's child
OL,15,Fwithout her mother.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
