CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784656151
OL,3,C'My girl had to die to be heard':
OL,4,CMum's plea for change in law
OL,6,F"My girl didn't want to die. My girl
OL,7,Fwanted to live. But she lived in
OL,8,Ffear," Angela said. "Every day I look
OL,9,Finto that little girl's eyes, her
OL,10,Fbaby, and I just wish that her mummy
OL,11,Fwas here for her, and she's not.
OL,13,F"Kiena had a right to live. She wasn't
OL,14,Fprotected by the people that she
OL,15,Fshould have been protected by."
OL,17,FAngela expressed pride that her
OL,18,Fdaughter tried repeatedly to seek
OL,19,Fhelp, but condemned the systemic
OL,20,Ffailures and victim-blaming Kiena
OL,21,Fexperienced.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784656151
OL,3,C'My girl had to die to be heard':
OL,4,CMum's plea for change in law
OL,6,FShe said: "Girls shouldn't have to die
OL,7,Fto be heard, and my daughter had to
OL,8,Fdie to be heard. There was so much
OL,9,Fvictim blaming.
OL,11,F"I'll always be Kiena's voice. I'll
OL,12,Falso be a voice not just for Kiena but
OL,13,Ffor the girls that have been lost as
OL,14,Fwell. My heart goes out to those
OL,15,Ffamilies."
OL,17,FRyan Wellings denied the manslaughter
OL,18,Fof Kiena Dawes and became the first
OL,19,Fdefendant to be tried before a jury
OL,20,Faccused of the unlawful killing of his
OL,21,Fpartner after her suicide.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
