OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784656151
OL,3,C'My girl had to die to be heard':
OL,4,CMum's plea for change in law
OL,6,FHe was acquitted of the charge, but
OL,7,Fwas found guilty of assault and
OL,8,Fprolonged domestic violence towards
OL,9,FKiena and jailed for six years in
OL,10,FJanuary 2025.
OL,12,FThe campaign for Kiena's Law is
OL,13,Fcalling for the creation of a
OL,14,Fstandalone offence for domestic abuse-
OL,15,Frelated suicide.
OL,17,FIt is also asking for in coercive and
OL,18,Fcontrolling behaviour to be included
OL,19,Fwithin the "dangerous offender"
OL,20,Fframework, allowing courts to impose
OL,21,Fextended sentences.
OL,26,@{D@LOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
