PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784656151
OL,3,C'My girl had to die to be heard':
OL,4,CMum's plea for change in law
OL,6,FAngela believes the proposed law could
OL,7,Fhelp save lives, with tens of
OL,8,Fthousands of people having already
OL,9,Fsigned the petition calling on
OL,10,FGovernment to act.
OL,12,F"Nothing is ever going to bring my
OL,13,Fbaby back, but if we can change things
OL,14,Fmoving forward, I'd hate to see
OL,15,Fanother family go through what we've
OL,16,Fbeen through," Angela added.
OL,18,F"Please don't give up, all of you who
OL,19,Fare working so hard for these changes.
OL,20,FLet's stop losing girls in this way."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
