FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784656151
OL,3,C'My girl had to die to be heard':
OL,4,CMum's plea for change in law
OL,6,FCampaigners and local leaders say
OL,7,FKiena's death highlighted a "serious
OL,8,Fblind spot" in the law.
OL,10,FFrank Mullane MBE, CEO of Advocacy
OL,11,FAfter Fatal Domestic Abuse (AAFDA),
OL,12,Fexplained: "Too often, when a victim
OL,13,Fdies by suicide following prolonged
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse, coercive control, and
OL,15,Fintimidation, the full impact of that
OL,16,Fabuse is not recognised by the
OL,17,Fcriminal justice system
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784656151
OL,3,C'My girl had to die to be heard':
OL,4,CMum's plea for change in law
OL,6,F"Kiena's Law represents an opportunity
OL,7,Fto recognise the devastating and
OL,8,Fsometimes fatal consequences of
OL,9,Fcoercive and controlling behaviour,
OL,10,Fimprove accountability, and help
OL,11,Fprevent future deaths."
OL,13,FLancashire's Police and Crime
OL,14,FCommissioner Clive Grunshaw added: "We
OL,15,Fmust continue to learn lessons,
OL,16,Fimprove protections for victims and
OL,17,Fensure that women and girls are
OL,18,Fsupported when they seek help.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
